```&lt;script&gt;
  require('.../module.js').then((module) =&gt; {
    module.init({{someDataFromHubSpotFields}}).run();
  })
&lt;/script&gt;```

Now I am doing this

```&lt;script&gt;
    window.__site_header_module__ = {{ module.auth_page_link|tojson }};
&lt;/script&gt;```

So I want to achieve this functional way, which will isolate all the data within function. Do you get the idea?
```&lt;script&gt;
  require('/path/to/my/module.js').then((module) =&gt; {
    module.init({{someDataFromHubSpotFieldsUsingHUBLBraces}}).run();
